Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--text--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.98,0:00:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  防禦的基礎和步法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.15,0:00:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.79,0:00:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帝國的語言
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.77,0:00:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  記得不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.88,0:00:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊  劍術的練習我倒是理解
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.18,0:00:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歷史和算術什麼的沒必要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.33,0:00:22.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.44,0:00:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的心情我理解  但只會劍術的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.06,0:00:27.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就成不了出色的劍士哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.25,0:00:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那個真是傑作
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.60,0:00:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾利露模仿得簡直和奧塔維亞一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.37,0:00:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧塔維亞也是  艾利露一這樣就沒轍了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.74,0:00:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨你…說
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.97,0:00:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.21,0:00:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…感覺好像有誰在看著這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.89,0:01:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錯覺嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.08,0:01:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧塔維亞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.22,0:01:11.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就如你們所願  來學習劍術吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.39,0:01:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.22,0:01:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯嘛  柯那魯  艾利露
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.66,0:01:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.72,0:01:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  排好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.39,0:01:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是正眼的架勢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.39,0:01:23.30,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正眼，劍術的一種基礎姿勢，用劍尖指著對方的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.69,0:01:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.68,0:03:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為劍士手下留情是禁忌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.87,0:03:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是對劍士名譽的最大侮辱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.69,0:04:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給余記住
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.78,0:04:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉蒂亞大人  偵查的士兵回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.74,0:04:09.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？  找到類似蠻族要塞的城堡了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.95,0:04:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  在森林深處  那一定是他們的大本營
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.00,0:04:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.58,0:04:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡的蠻族  別以為用結界就能瞞過余
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.58,0:04:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外  發現有個像是帝國士兵的金髮女性在蠻族當中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.55,0:04:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聚集士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.82,0:04:29.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.50,0:04:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不給我致命一擊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.76,0:04:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這混蛋  要侮辱我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.75,0:04:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.30,0:04:55.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.11,0:04:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧塔維亞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.45,0:05:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後一個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.99,0:05:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近在阿瓦隆周圍頻繁發現疑似帝國士兵的可疑人影
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.65,0:05:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請加強警戒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.09,0:05:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的會議到此結束
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.92,0:05:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.35,0:05:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小摩我已經肚子空空了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.41,0:05:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧  阿爾撒魯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.15,0:05:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  阿爾撒魯我也…空空了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.23,0:05:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧伽姆我也空空了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.41,0:05:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位  夜宵準備好了  請前往食堂用餐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.48,0:05:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿瓦隆城堡蛋糕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.80,0:05:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔  真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.36,0:05:50.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  要吃個飽哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.66,0:05:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  奧塔維亞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.90,0:05:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧塔維亞小姐的話  說是有事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.98,0:05:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.55,0:06:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿隆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.62,0:06:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.34,0:06:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.06,0:06:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧塔維亞和帝國士兵？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.58,0:06:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在森林中狩獵的戰士好像看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.73,0:06:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這裡也有一些類似的報告
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.46,0:06:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.85,0:06:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摩爾嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.08,0:06:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧塔維亞是夥伴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.78,0:06:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她怎麼會和敵人見面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.13,0:06:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜點  摩爾嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.79,0:06:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.28,0:06:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.78,0:06:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.96,0:06:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有開始懷疑的人存在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.89,0:06:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很簡單嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.60,0:06:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查清楚不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.61,0:06:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.75,0:06:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去直接問她確認
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.83,0:06:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  等…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.41,0:07:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小摩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.59,0:07:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿隆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.88,0:07:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.88,0:07:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.13,0:07:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  明明聽說是在這附近看到的說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.89,0:07:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是帝國士兵…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.68,0:07:39.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧塔維亞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.75,0:07:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摩爾嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.06,0:07:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從森林裡回來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.75,0:07:47.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去做什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.40,0:07:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劍術的練習
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.96,0:07:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.93,0:07:53.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.37,0:08:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶吶  這個怎麼讀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.68,0:08:03.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好難啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.80,0:08:07.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小摩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.56,0:08:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都沒發生哦  什麼都沒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.74,0:08:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧塔維亞的事啊  她只是去練習劍術了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.62,0:08:18.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大半夜一個人？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.11,0:08:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  她是個「裸奔」的傢伙嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.11,0:08:21.42,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摩爾嘉大概是想說Striking（引人注目）但念成了Streaking（裸奔）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.04,0:08:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禁慾？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.04,0:08:24.00,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果莉安瓏理解成了Stoic（禁慾）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.01,0:08:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.76,0:08:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是我還得去下艾柏娜那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.96,0:08:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  摩爾嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.07,0:08:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲  阿爾撒魯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.18,0:08:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在金魚那裡  一個人練劍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.18,0:08:32.64,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摩爾嘉開始亂讀了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.94,0:08:35.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摩爾嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.53,0:08:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金子裡有魚啊！哎呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.53,0:08:38.45,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,語無倫次了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.09,0:08:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.54,0:08:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小摩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.64,0:08:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.70,0:08:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.63,0:08:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧塔維亞  快點快點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.95,0:08:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.08,0:09:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去採果子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.16,0:09:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去採一個很厲害的蘑菇哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.32,0:09:05.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘑菇？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.61,0:09:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要帶他們出城外嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.96,0:09:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.04,0:09:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  摩爾嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.79,0:09:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們只是去去森林而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.81,0:09:15.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要找夢幻的蘑菇  柯那魯想找到它
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.78,0:09:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想給奧塔維亞看看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.68,0:09:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是奧塔維亞的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.70,0:09:25.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我們說想要去的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.71,0:09:27.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常美味的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.80,0:09:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  是我錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.15,0:09:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我也考慮欠妥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.66,0:09:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後我會注意的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.49,0:09:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.93,0:09:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.94,0:09:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.82,0:09:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美味的說…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.57,0:09:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.41,0:09:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摩爾嘉那傢伙怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.15,0:09:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然不讓去森林
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.36,0:09:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我們的秘密基地中找到了哦  夢幻的蘑菇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.38,0:10:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們差不多要行動了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.23,0:10:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.29,0:10:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然知道他們就潛伏在周圍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.14,0:10:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不賣個破綻的話就不能把他們引出來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.80,0:10:19.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們害得你被罵了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.36,0:10:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一定會找到夢幻的蘑菇給奧塔維亞的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.96,0:10:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以原諒我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.43,0:10:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.00,0:10:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們有那個心意我就很高興了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.04,0:10:36.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是吃了非常美味的夢幻的蘑菇的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.34,0:10:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧塔維亞一定會更高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.36,0:10:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能答應我一件事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.71,0:10:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近千萬不要兩個人走出城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.13,0:10:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.52,0:10:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能答應我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.36,0:10:57.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.42,0:11:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是莉姆莉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.38,0:11:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候打擾真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.96,0:11:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子有些話無論如何都要跟您說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.88,0:11:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為一直都睡不著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.91,0:11:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡不著？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.38,0:11:24.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜下來了嗎  艾露敏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.85,0:11:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.31,0:11:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是聽不到昆蟲的聲音了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.78,0:11:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昆蟲的聲音？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.14,0:11:37.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昆蟲先生們真是偷懶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.90,0:11:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有夜晚的音樂就睡不著了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.38,0:11:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷懶的昆蟲們是在什麼方向的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.21,0:11:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.73,0:11:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是大功一件哦  艾露敏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.66,0:11:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  國王大人  艾露敏立什麼功了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.20,0:12:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  真是幫大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.07,0:12:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上讓你再次聽到夜晚的音樂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.67,0:12:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國王大人  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.52,0:12:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧伽姆  立刻召集戰士們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.50,0:12:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.67,0:12:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾利露  找到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.16,0:12:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.16,0:12:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是被別人采走了呢  夢幻的蘑菇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.07,0:12:29.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續找吧  一定還有的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.31,0:12:32.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾利露
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.45,0:12:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開艾利露
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.71,0:12:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要救她的話就去告訴那個女帝國士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.44,0:12:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓她深夜到這裡來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.50,0:12:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把艾利露…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.61,0:12:47.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事不許和任何人說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.11,0:12:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說了的話會怎麼樣知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.27,0:12:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把艾利露還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.64,0:13:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯那魯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.29,0:13:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我不好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.78,0:13:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明約好…不去城堡外面的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.82,0:13:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.97,0:13:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是最後通牒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.02,0:13:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶我們進城
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.79,0:13:27.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拒絕的話你身邊的人就會遇上不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.59,0:13:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.04,0:13:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我很急
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.33,0:13:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.32,0:13:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.25,0:13:49.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說點什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.22,0:13:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼什麼都不說  我們是夥伴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.95,0:14:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夥伴之間總是互相幫助的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.54,0:14:09.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.03,0:14:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.31,0:14:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我要相信你到最後
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.64,0:14:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摩爾嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.14,0:14:25.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是個大丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.07,0:14:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是女的！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.95,0:14:41.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧塔維亞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.81,0:14:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見  奧塔維亞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.31,0:14:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉蒂亞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.84,0:14:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在近衛兵預選隊的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.43,0:14:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野營時也度過了好幾個這樣的雨天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.52,0:15:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候我們的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.92,0:15:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是為了帝國戰鬥  成為理想中的劍士
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.81,0:15:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要做這樣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.81,0:15:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要背叛帝國！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.78,0:15:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你踐踏了余的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.13,0:15:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而那個時候…侮辱了神聖的決鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.26,0:15:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當余知道  你由於父親的過錯而不能成為近衛兵的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.12,0:15:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然覺得不公平
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.53,0:15:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但既然是元老院的決議  也無可奈何
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.29,0:15:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以至少在你離開前  想舉行一場劍士之間的決鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.02,0:15:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓墮落腐化的元老院
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.79,0:15:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看真正貴族的生存之道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.06,0:15:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.11,0:15:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不給我致命一擊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.11,0:15:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使這樣你還是不給余致命一擊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.23,0:16:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓余背負恥辱苟且偷生  你卻拂袖而去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.76,0:16:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.86,0:16:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.90,0:16:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾利露就還給我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.44,0:16:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.99,0:16:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.93,0:16:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧塔維亞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.83,0:16:24.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你受驚了  已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.86,0:16:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧塔維亞  你說錯了是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.80,0:16:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧塔維亞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.99,0:16:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答余  奧塔維亞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.66,0:16:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回城堡去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.48,0:16:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去  去把夥伴們叫來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.74,0:16:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了  把你捲進來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.17,0:16:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夥伴之間總是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.44,0:16:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,互相幫助！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.97,0:16:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.51,0:16:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾撒魯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.86,0:17:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們算清之前的帳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.98,0:17:09.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殲滅他們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.73,0:17:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繞向右側  把敵人分開
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.79,0:17:17.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摩爾嘉  瞄準敵人的副將
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.24,0:17:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.95,0:17:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微活動一下身子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.71,0:17:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.04,0:17:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的問題還沒回答吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.31,0:17:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.62,0:17:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在生活在與帝國想法不同的夥伴當中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.52,0:17:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然還不徹底  但我的思考方式已經在逐漸改變
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.08,0:18:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼是美麗的  什麼是醜惡的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.24,0:18:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人為了什麼而活
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.76,0:18:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名譽究竟是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.93,0:18:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.86,0:18:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決定原諒你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.41,0:18:14.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.13,0:18:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你  莉蒂亞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.27,0:18:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你這混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.75,0:18:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能！  因為猶豫沒有下手的  難道是余嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.69,0:18:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該感到羞恥的不是我  而是你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.23,0:18:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.16,0:19:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.17,0:20:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧塔…維亞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.25,0:20:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爾和余…是完美的…是真正的劍士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.06,0:20:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.83,0:20:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  你說的沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.63,0:20:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是完美的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.31,0:20:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是真正的劍士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.85,0:20:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧塔維亞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.50,0:21:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉蒂亞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.43,0:21:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是很早就知道的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.42,0:21:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.63,0:21:19.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.31,0:21:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是喜歡我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.61,0:21:31.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是離開帝國後才發覺的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.87,0:21:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.26,0:21:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰都不忍心殺死對方！


